{
  "texts": [
    "On the other hand, BERT was employed to extract the aspect and opinion terms.",
    "A linear layer is then used to combine the extracted features.",
    "The second model, HGCN-BERT+BERT-TFM, is similar but replaces the final stacked layer with a transformer block (BERT-TFM).",
    "Zhang et al. (2021a) introduced these two baseline models for comparison with his proposed TASO-BERT-Linear, TASO-BERT-CRF, GAS (Zhang et al. 2021d) and PAR-APHRASE (Zhang et al. 2021a) model, aiming to demonstrate the superiority of the PARAPHRASE model.",
    "Later, Hu et al. (2022) compared these models with dataset-level order (DLO) and instance-level order (ILO) methods and demonstrated that DLO and ILO achieve better performance in ACOSQE task."
  ]
}